(text "NOTES:" (at 20.32 309.88 0) (effects (font (size 1.27 1.27))) (uuid a8f8f49d-f303-5399-931a-c2a40c61abc7))
(text "J80 high-speed pins follow the Mu eDP source connector; power/backlight pins are not pass-through to avoid backfeed." (at 20.32 317.5 0) (effects (font (size 1.27 1.27))) (uuid 0b8614e6-fc36-56ed-8776-1a68e950e167))
(text "J81 follows the 40-pin eDP pinout in gen/Pinouts_README.md: lanes 3..0, AUX, HPD, LCD_3V3, BL_PWR, BL_EN/PWM." (at 20.32 325.12 0) (effects (font (size 1.27 1.27))) (uuid 5e676a6e-e502-54bc-a164-7ea1f1cab141))
(text "J82 provides the reference I2C touch pinout; keep the separate USB touch header if the reused 16in panel uses USB touch." (at 20.32 332.74 0) (effects (font (size 1.27 1.27))) (uuid fe3acbf4-86b7-54ec-9269-da6f44228d7e))
(text "Exact J80/J81 mechanical footprints and cable orientation still need the real panel/controller hardware on the bench." (at 20.32 340.36 0) (effects (font (size 1.27 1.27))) (uuid 799253f9-2c7a-5df0-ad10-9eb33c25912c))
